# Gen-Z Features Walkthrough

## Features Implemented

All 7 Gen-Z demo features have been successfully implemented and verified:

### 1. 🌈 Vibe Themes
- **7 theme presets**: Default, Sunset Chill, Neon Rave, Lo-Fi Study, Midnight, Cozy Night, Ocean Breeze
- Smooth CSS transitions between themes
- Theme picker in header (palette icon)
- Persists selection via localStorage

### 2. 👻 Ghost Mode
- Toggle switch in header
- Hides online status and typing indicators
- Shows "Ghost Mode Active" banner when enabled
- Toast notification on toggle

### 3. ⏱️ Self-Destructing Messages
- Bomb icon opens timer selector (5s, 10s, 30s, 1m)
- Countdown animation on messages
- Blur/fade destroy effect with smoke particles

### 4. 🎁 Digital Gifts
- Gift picker modal with 9 gifts (Rose, Pizza, Coffee, Hug, Cake, Diamond, Fire, Star, Rainbow)
- Full-screen flying emoji animation
- Gift appears as special message type

### 5. 💕 Vibe Reactions
- Extended reaction picker (Fire, Dead, Cap, Slay, Vibe, Grass)
- Reaction animations on messages

### 6. 🔥 Streaks & Milestones
- Streak badges next to contact names
- Confetti celebration for milestones

### 7. 🎲 Mini-Games
- Game picker with 4 games: Coin Flip, Dice Roll, Truth or Dare, Would You Rather
- Interactive SweetAlert modals for gameplay
- Results shown as chat messages

